{"tid":2049383,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"6月3日 士兵到首都地區實行戒嚴","createTime":"2020-06-03T12:02:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-03T13:06:37.000Z","uid":153701,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6ef1b136e64a7673335b61c750d02a801878df32","tid":2049383,"uid":153701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T12:02:56.000Z","msg":"美國非裔男子弗洛伊德死亡後，多個城市連續第八晚有民眾示威，與前幾晚比較，相對和平。<br />\n<br />\n得州休斯敦有6萬人抗議，包括弗洛伊德多名家人。休斯敦是弗洛伊德成長地，他下周在當地下葬。<br />\n<br />\n紐約有數千人在宵禁令後上街，曼哈頓交通受阻，片段顯示人群包圍一輛警車。紐約的宵禁延長至星期日，並提前在晚上8時實施。<br />\n<br />\n洛杉磯、費城、阿特蘭大和西雅圖等城市亦有大型集會和遊行。<br />\n<br />\n連日來全國的示威活動，至少9300人被捕。五角大樓調動1600名士兵到首都華盛頓地區戒備。"},{"pid":"b68e48626b419007ab0dd45b01fbe3f0fd4d69c0","tid":2049383,"uid":127929,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T12:07:42.000Z","msg":"1600個?<br />\n<br />\n香港普通和理唱都出6000隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b4baab021acccc323bd794bc48c64dc6bd6cc1b","tid":2049383,"uid":261505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b68e48626b419007ab0dd45b01fbe3f0fd4d69c0","tid":2049383,"uid":127929,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T12:07:42.000Z","msg":"1600個?<br />\n<br />\n香港普通和理唱都出6000隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T12:14:31.000Z","msg":"士兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6877f87ac21b507c843b27865fadf22755a6020","tid":2049383,"uid":60527,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T13:00:21.000Z","msg":"聽日屠城？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc059693f7d1bce7f4541c236ba8b9f38d889e9c","tid":2049383,"uid":66087,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T13:01:42.000Z","msg":"真心希望唔會出大事<br />\n<br />\n唔係以後一講六四就變美國士兵鎮壓人民 <img src=\"/a